headline: Anne Bramman Elected to Morningstar’s Board of Directors
summary: CHICAGO, January 05, 2026--Morningstar, Inc. (Nasdaq: MORN), a leading provider of independent investment insights, today announced that Anne Bramman has been elected to Morningstar’s board of directors. Bramman currently serves as a board director and audit committee chair at McCormick & Company and as a senior advisor at Boston Consulting Group.

headline: What to Expect From Avery Dennison's Q4 2025 Earnings Report
summary: Avery Dennison is set to announce its fourth-quarter results soon, with analysts projecting single-digit growth in its bottom-line figure.
